          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-layout-1-multirow-img-01.webp",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "OUR VALUES",
            "text": "<p>We are focused as a company on the idea of more eco and less ego.<br/>The brands we feature have all paved the way for sustainability in swimwear, with their collections featuring a variety of textiles including recycled, organic, and plant-based fabrics.</p><p>Not limited by age, size or shape, wearing swimwear that fits, feels good, and frees her to be the woman she’s meant to be.</p>",
            "button_label": "VIEW More",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections"
          }
        },
        "row_GTRaEF": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-layout-1-multirow-img-02.webp",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "OUR PROMISE",
            "text": "<p>Committed to sustainability from the ground up. From recycled packaging, fibers, and even earth-inspired prints. Because we think swimwear should help clean up our waters, not pollute them.</p><p>Inspired by exotic travel destinations and the bold colors of the beach, our swimwear designs never go out of style. No matter your shape or size, there’s a selection of suits to find your perfect fit.</p>",
            "button_label": "VIEW MORE",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/all"
          }
        }
      },
